data.description: Discover hassle-free living in this move-in-ready 3-bedroom townhome featuring a private backyard & a 2-car garage. The well-designed open floor plan welcomes you w/ vaulted ceilings & a cozy fireplace in living area. The kitchen is equipped w/ a brand-new refrigerator & dishwasher. Enjoy the comfort of newer carpet throughout the main floor, where you'll find a guest bathroom, 2nd bedroom & primary suite, which offers a 3/4 bathroom & a spacious walk-in closet. The finished lower level includes a family room, a laundry room, & a generously sized 3rd bedroom. Benefit from the association fee covering essential services such as snow removal, lawn care, trash removal, & exterior house painting approximately every 5 years. Additionally, the community ensures a well-maintained environment w/ sprinklers & common area upkeep. Conveniently situated w/ fast access to the interstate, this turn-key townhome provides not just a residence but a lifestyle that embraces comfort and convenience.
